Author: Tommy Reeves
Content:
Buy organic strawberries whenever possible.
Wash strawberries thoroughly under running water before eating.
Remove any visible blemishes or mold.
Limit consumption of strawberries from sources with a history of pesticide or heavy metal contamination.
Store strawberries properly in the refrigerator.
